📱 2. CREATE APK (Android App)

We’ll use Expo (simple & fast)

🚀 Step 1: Install Expo
npm install -g expo-cli
🚀 Step 2: Build APK

Inside your mobile folder:

expo build:android

OR (new method):

npx expo prebuild
npx expo run:android

👉 Expo will give:

Download APK link
🔥 Important Fix

Replace this in App.js:

fetch("https://your-app.onrender.com/predict")
